flowRoot.flowPara: The goal of the project is to create a minimalist, useful, cross platform C compiler. I'd like to see...C11 Compatibility.Both Windows and *nix work equally well.Zero config toolchain builds.Zero config cross compilation (Or as close as possible, this includes support libraries like libc).Toolchain builds in the blink of an eye (I usually take a nap between GCC/Clang builds).Good documentation and a low learning curve.A companion assembler/linker to remove the dependence on binutils.Aggressive removal of cruft.An SSA optimizing backend AFTER feature completion.Compilation of Go1.4 so we can bootstrap ourselves.
